Roger Crockett is a thought leadership advisor, veteran writer, and a speaker on business leadership and diversity. He is the former Chicago Deputy Bureau Chief for BusinessWeek magazine and a contributor to Harvard Business Review online. This site delivers exclusive insight from and about some of the most influential leaders in business.
